It was consuming me
completely, and I

00:35:34.169 --> 00:35:35.960 align:middle line:84%
couldn't stop thinking,
well-- so I started

00:35:35.960 --> 00:35:37.900 align:middle line:84%
thinking about this, and that,
and how would prostitution

