I'm not kidding you, because
then your brain starts

00:35:45.540 --> 00:35:48.400 align:middle line:84%
to play all these tricks
on you, and you realize

00:35:48.400 --> 00:35:50.290 align:middle line:84%
that the more questions
you've answered

00:35:50.290 --> 00:35:53.480 align:middle line:84%
the easier it is to answer
