Any problem that we have
in the world today gets

00:36:02.890 --> 00:36:06.250 align:middle line:84%
answered and solved
virtually instantly

00:36:06.250 --> 00:36:08.270 align:middle line:84%
if you just remove
money from the system.

00:36:08.270 --> 00:36:13.140 align:middle line:84%
So this is why, I
guess, I started

00:36:13.140 --> 00:36:15.700 align:middle line:84%
formulating this philosophy,
and it just grew, and grew,

00:36:15.700 --> 00:36:18.410 align:middle line:84%
and grew, and the UBUNTU
movement came out of it,

00:36:18.410 --> 00:36:20.390 align:middle line:84%
because I realized that
this ancient knowledge

00:36:20.390 --> 00:36:23.280 align:middle line:84%
and philosophy is
enshrined and encoded

00:36:23.280 --> 00:36:25.920 align:middle line:90%
in this word called UBUNTU.

00:36:25.920 --> 00:36:28.560 align:middle line:84%
So what is UBUNTU and
what does it mean?

00:36:28.560 --> 00:36:30.260 align:middle line:84%
Well, like I
mentioned earlier, it

00:36:30.260 --> 00:36:32.700 align:middle line:84%
is an ancient
African philosophy,

00:36:32.700 --> 00:36:34.910 align:middle line:84%
but it's not just an
ancient African philosophy.

00:36:34.910 --> 00:36:37.250 align:middle line:84%
It's an ancient
global philosophy.

00:36:37.250 --> 00:36:40.880 align:middle line:84%
All ancient cultures
have the same philosophy,

00:36:40.880 --> 00:36:43.940 align:middle line:84%
and in a nutshell, it means
unity within community.

00:36:43.940 --> 00:36:46.570 align:middle line:84%
That's probably
the best definition

00:36:46.570 --> 00:36:51.460 align:middle line:84%
that I've been able to find
for this word, UBUNTU-- unity

00:36:51.460 --> 00:36:54.530 align:middle line:84%
within community where everybody
works towards the greatest

00:36:54.530 --> 00:36:56.990 align:middle line:84%
benefit of all in
their community

00:36:56.990 --> 00:37:01.190 align:middle line:84%
by contributing their
talents and their skills

00:37:01.190 --> 00:37:03.770 align:middle line:84%
to be used and
available to everyone.

00:37:03.770 --> 00:37:07.630 align:middle line:84%
Not just for you, or you, or
you a one to one exchange.

00:37:07.630 --> 00:37:09.370 align:middle line:90%
It's a one to many exchange.

00:37:09.370 --> 00:37:12.100 align:middle line:84%
Whatever I do is
available to everyone

00:37:12.100 --> 00:37:16.070 align:middle line:84%
to benefit from, and therein
lies the fundamental difference

00:37:16.070 --> 00:37:19.010 align:middle line:84%
about many of the
other ideas of barter,

00:37:19.010 --> 00:37:21.990 align:middle line:84%
and trade, and exchange
that some people are

00:37:21.990 --> 00:37:23.590 align:middle line:90%
out there sharing.

00:37:23.590 --> 00:37:25.920 align:middle line:84%
So the Contributionism
philosophy

00:37:25.920 --> 00:37:30.030 align:middle line:84%
is just a modern word
that I came up with

00:37:30.030 --> 00:37:34.170 align:middle line:84%
to try and describe this ancient
philosophy called UBUNTU,

00:37:34.170 --> 00:37:37.070 align:middle line:84%
and I've made up this
word because of the fact

00:37:37.070 --> 00:37:40.300 align:middle line:84%
that you're contributing
your skills.

00:37:40.300 --> 00:37:42.130 align:middle line:90%
It's your contribution.

00:37:42.130 --> 00:37:46.480 align:middle line:84%
So although in the
beginning there

00:37:46.480 --> 00:37:48.450 align:middle line:90%
was many debates about the ism.

00:37:48.450 --> 00:37:52.194 align:middle line:84%
It's another Contributionism,
and I was quite opposed to it

00:37:52.194 --> 00:37:53.860 align:middle line:84%
to start out with,
but somehow it stuck.

00:37:53.860 --> 00:37:55.234 align:middle line:84%
We couldn't come
up with a better

00:37:55.234 --> 00:37:57.370 align:middle line:90%
word than Contributionism.

00:37:57.370 --> 00:37:59.780 align:middle line:84%
So the way I'd like
to describe it--

00:37:59.780 --> 00:38:01.700 align:middle line:84%
it is like no other
ism we've ever

00:38:01.700 --> 00:38:05.830 align:middle line:84%
had before, because
all the other isms have

00:38:05.830 --> 00:38:07.540 align:middle line:90%
money attached to them.

00:38:07.540 --> 00:38:10.460 align:middle line:84%
This is the only ism that I
know of where we remove money

00:38:10.460 --> 00:38:14.070 align:middle line:84%
from the system, so it
becomes a Contributionism,

00:38:14.070 --> 00:38:17.870 align:middle line:84%
a whole new way of looking at
how we co-exist, and share,

00:38:17.870 --> 00:38:20.930 align:middle line:84%
and create abundance
for ourselves,

00:38:20.930 --> 00:38:22.760 align:middle line:90%
and abundance beyond belief.

00:38:22.760 --> 00:38:27.120 align:middle line:84%
So it is really proposing
a world without money.

00:38:27.120 --> 00:38:28.760 align:middle line:90%
This is what it's all about.

00:38:28.760 --> 00:38:30.620 align:middle line:90%
We have to get rid of the money.

00:38:30.620 --> 00:38:33.180 align:middle line:84%
We cannot beat about the
bush, or be nice about it,

00:38:33.180 --> 00:38:34.810 align:middle line:90%
or be polite about it.

00:38:34.810 --> 00:38:36.150 align:middle line:90%
Money is the problem.

00:38:36.150 --> 00:38:38.210 align:middle line:84%
We've got to get rid
of it, because those

00:38:38.210 --> 00:38:40.460 align:middle line:84%
that control the
money will continue

00:38:40.460 --> 00:38:43.520 align:middle line:84%
using that tool as a
tool of enslavement,

00:38:43.520 --> 00:38:45.380 align:middle line:84%
and as long as they've
got the controlling

00:38:45.380 --> 00:38:47.110 align:middle line:84%
power over this
tool, there's very

00:38:47.110 --> 00:38:49.380 align:middle line:84%
little we're going to
be able to do about it.

00:38:49.380 --> 00:38:53.000 align:middle line:84%
So if we don't use
the money, they

00:38:53.000 --> 00:38:55.210 align:middle line:90%
have no more control over us.

00:38:55.210 --> 00:38:57.120 align:middle line:90%
It really is that simple.

00:38:57.120 --> 00:39:00.950 align:middle line:84%
If we don't need their money,
how can they control us?

00:39:00.950 --> 00:39:04.770 align:middle line:84%
So just let me plant
that seed with you.

00:39:04.770 --> 00:39:07.730 align:middle line:84%
If you don't need their
money to get on with anything

00:39:07.730 --> 00:39:10.230 align:middle line:84%
you do in life, whether it's
creating technology, or growing

00:39:10.230 --> 00:39:14.490 align:middle line:84%
food, or building your
homes, or creating healing.

00:39:14.490 --> 00:39:16.780 align:middle line:84%
If we don't need their
money-- I say their

00:39:16.780 --> 00:39:18.996 align:middle line:84%
because the money
we use is not ours.

00:39:18.996 --> 00:39:20.870 align:middle line:84%
The money in your bank
doesn't belong to you.

00:39:20.870 --> 00:39:22.434 align:middle line:90%
It belongs to the bank.

00:39:22.434 --> 00:39:24.100 align:middle line:84%
They're the ones that
created the money.

00:39:24.100 --> 00:39:26.030 align:middle line:84%
Even the pieces of paper
don't belong to you.

00:39:26.030 --> 00:39:27.500 align:middle line:84%
You think it belongs to you
because it's in your wallet.

00:39:27.500 --> 00:39:28.940 align:middle line:90%
It doesn't belong to you.

00:39:28.940 --> 00:39:31.770 align:middle line:84%
It's always belongs to
the bank, and the moment

00:39:31.770 --> 00:39:34.140 align:middle line:84%
you deposit it in the
bank it's no longer yours.

00:39:34.140 --> 00:39:35.480 align:middle line:90%
It's the bank's money.

00:39:35.480 --> 00:39:37.020 align:middle line:90%
They're holding it for you.

00:39:37.020 --> 00:39:39.990 align:middle line:84%
We're moving from a
money driven society

00:39:39.990 --> 00:39:43.010 align:middle line:84%
to a society driven by
people, their talents,

00:39:43.010 --> 00:39:46.240 align:middle line:84%
and their passion for life
where everyone contributes

00:39:46.240 --> 00:39:50.250 align:middle line:84%
their natural talents or their
acquired skills to the greatest

00:39:50.250 --> 00:39:53.070 align:middle line:84%
benefit of all in
their community.

00:39:53.070 --> 00:39:55.710 align:middle line:84%
That's what we are
laying out here today.

00:39:55.710 --> 00:39:57.640 align:middle line:84%
This is the foundation
we're building

00:39:57.640 --> 00:40:03.180 align:middle line:84%
and the simple steps towards
this new world of abundance.

00:40:03.180 --> 00:40:08.760 align:middle line:84%
So the five point mantra of
Contributionism something

00:40:08.760 --> 00:40:09.560 align:middle line:90%
that evolved.

00:40:09.560 --> 00:40:14.000 align:middle line:84%
Again, it's something that
evolved over a 10 year period

00:40:14.000 --> 00:40:16.570 align:middle line:90%
or maybe a few lesser years.

00:40:16.570 --> 00:40:17.670 align:middle line:90%
No money.

00:40:17.670 --> 00:40:18.830 align:middle line:90%
No barter.

00:40:18.830 --> 00:40:20.270 align:middle line:90%
No trade.

00:40:20.270 --> 00:40:23.860 align:middle line:84%
No value attached to anything
greater than anything else,

00:40:23.860 --> 00:40:25.710 align:middle line:84%
and a system where
everyone contributes

00:40:25.710 --> 00:40:27.860 align:middle line:84%
their natural talents
